.idea/
.claude/
.junie/
.python-version

# Converter staging output (regenerable from the JSON sources)
**/_generated/

# Python bytecode caches (regenerable)
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# Browser/auth session state — contains live credentials, never commit
**/auth_state.json

# Misplaced-paste junk (PyCharm/BetterVoting drops). These keep getting auto-staged;
# ignore them so they never land in a commit. `scripts/check_repo_hygiene.py` (run by
# the pre-commit hook) still WARNS about them, so a real file pasted with a wrong name
# isn't silently lost — see CLAUDE.md for the img/<bv_id>_*.png and *_bv_export.json rules.
**/Ballot Data*.json
**/img_[0-9]*.png
**/image_[0-9]*.png
**/Screenshot*.png
**/Screen Shot*.png
**/* - Copy*

# Generated search outputs from the divergence-finder tools (regenerable)
**/star_irv_hits.csv
**/four_way_hits.csv
**/star_irv_divergence_*.csv
**/star_irv_divergence_*_ballots.txt
**/*_ballots.txt
**/star_irv_log.txt
**/four_way_log.txt
